{"tid":1044402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳男子橡筋帶上吊亡","createTime":"2019-03-03T00:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T00:51:39.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ffc1210974facc2312d7ff1f8c33a812445e2679","tid":1044402,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T00:42:47.000Z","msg":"將軍澳廣場男子自縊亡。昨日(2日)晚上8時許，一名54歲姓陳男子在上址一單位走廊內，用橡筋帶纏頸上吊，其53歲姓袁妻子發現，立即將橡筋帶剪斷，報警求助。救護員到場，將昏迷事主送院搶救，惜證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方在現場未有檢獲遺書，初步調查相信事件無可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190303/bkn-20190303021145822-0303_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190303%2Fbkn-20190303021145822-0303_00822_001.html&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEIhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=68b2fa3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190303/bkn-20190303021145822-0303_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e905b60e6460ae39d5ec440b0df8820f26a5715b","tid":1044402,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T00:46:54.000Z","msg":"隔離左右上上下下多謝哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f997f9f0d3397d4e5a6d09f20cafe5b7c16e53","tid":1044402,"uid":10692,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T00:49:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70748e1ff3a0798ef690ef3b4d3841e2b64e3901","tid":1044402,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T00:51:35.000Z","msg":"奶波魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e53939191e64a6fd2fbdce093fb53ec60f371d0","tid":1044402,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T00:51:39.000Z","msg":"私樓撚自殺數字 好似同 公屋撚打個5 5 開<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}